    "The first part was used to gather the profile of the learners which are age, sex, parents' educational attainment, dialect, gadget/s available at home and the online application/s used.",
    "The second part was the inventory questionnaire to identify the attitude of the respondents towards the use of Artificial Intelligence (AI) in writing composition.",
    "Each item consists of statement to measure their attitudes through 5-point Likert scale.",
    "Upon their completion of the questionnaires, these were retrieved for calculation, tabulation, interpretation and analysis.",
    "Moreover, a written test was also established to determine the written discourse performances of learners."
